'''Baihong''' ({{zh|白宏}}) is a [[Hanoish languages|Southern]] [[Loloish language]] of [[Yunnan]], China. It is spoken in [[Jiangcheng Hani and Yi Autonomous County]], [[Mojiang Hani Autonomous County]], [[Yuanjiang Hani, Yi and Dai Autonomous County]], [[Lüchun County]], and [[Yuanyang County, Yunnan]].
