* The rural variety monophthongizes {{IPA|/iə, yə, uə/}} to {{IPA|[{{IPA link|eː}}, {{IPA link|øː}}, {{IPA link|oː}}]}}.{{sfnp|Heijmans|Gussenhoven|1998|p=107}}
* The first elements of {{IPA|/uə, ʌu/}} are somewhat centralized ({{IPA|[ü, ʌ̈]}}, respectively), but are not central enough to be labelled as central. Among these, the first element of {{IPA|/œy/}} is the most strongly centralized.{{sfnp|Heijmans|Gussenhoven|1998|p=110}}
* The second elements of {{IPA|/ɛi, œy, ʌu/}} are mid-centralized ({{IPA|[ɪ, ʏ, ʊ]}}, respectively).{{sfnp|Heijmans|Gussenhoven|1998|p=110}}
